<p>231 as it stands disgusts me. The whale joke is a way of tolerating it, because it's ridiculous and bizarre and horrible and all the more horrible because you laugh at it. That, and it doesn't involve child rape. The premise of &quot;they're raping a whale&quot; is still horrible, but its an exaggerated horrible, rather than a banal one, and it drops its pretension at the same time.</p>
